        "title": "Falling Action",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above This Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Beginning of Act 3:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Falling Action explores the aftermath of the Climax and its consequences for the Protagonist. If they escaped their dire situation or stole something, they may have enemies chasing after them. If they lost an important item, they might be facing the challenge of recovering it. After the darkest moment, the Protagonist is fully committed to resolving the Central Conflict and defeating the Antagonist. The tension increases as things seem to worsen for the Protagonist, but there is a glimmer of hope."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "How has the fallout from the Climax has changed the perspective of the Protagonist?"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "What drove them to commit fully to the challenge before them?"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Continue adding stress and pressure on the Protagonist as they work toward the story's final confrontation."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Offer any final exposition through flashbacks and dialogue."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Demonstrate how the Protagonist is using all they have learned and acquired to resolve the Central Conflict."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Keep the suspense/tension high to ensure the reader stays engaged through the end."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
