        "title": "Climax",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above This Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "End of Act 2:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "In this beat, the story naturally approaches the Climax, brings the reader back to the opening scene, and offers the resolution to the opening scene while leading to the story's Falling Action. The Climax is the turning point of the story and the Protagonist. The fallout from the Climax changes the Protagonist's perspective for the remainder of the story and often leaves them at their darkest moment, where all seems lost."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Bring the reader back to the opening scene and provide an exciting and satisfying solution to the Climax. "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Address the story's Central Conflict and demonstrate the fate of the Protagonist."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "How does the Climax impact the Protagonist's internal/external goals and overall transformation?"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 2 makes up 50% of the story from 25% - 75%."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Climax occurs around the 50% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
