        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "Rising Action",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above This Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Beginning of Act 2:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The story now enters the Rising Action, where the Protagonist faces challenges and obstacles on their way to the Climax. Each challenge or obstacle leads the Protagonist closer and closer to the dire situation the reader found them in at the beginning of the story. The action, tension, and stakes continue to rise as the Protagonist is put through their paces, and more context is given via Exposition. As with traditional story outlines, the Protagonist will face successes, failures, and setbacks along the way, teaching them and helping them grow."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Create a series of challenges and obstacles for the Protagonist – some will be overcome, while others will make things worse for the Protagonist as they learn and grow from them."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Consider how these steps lead to the Climax."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "How do the challenges and obstacles impact the Protagonist's story arc, goals, and motivations?"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Tantalize the reader as the tension rises and the story climbs closer to the opening scene. "
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 2 makes up 50% of the story from 25% - 75%."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Rising Action occurs around the 25% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
